# Rocket.new — Integrations Expert Reference (Web)

## How to Connect Any Integration
1. **Via chat**: "Connect [service] to my project" — Rocket prompts for API key
2. **Via Project Settings**: Open project → Settings → Integrations → select service
3. API keys are encrypted at rest and never exposed in generated code
4. Disconnect: Project Settings → Integrations → Disconnect

