## 📧 EMAIL SERVICES

### Which to Recommend
| Service | Best For | Free Tier |
|---|---|---|
| **Resend** | Developer-first transactional email | 3,000/month |
| **SendGrid** | High volume, marketing + transactional | 100/day |
| **Brevo** | All-in-one email + marketing automation | 300/day |
| **MailerLite** | Newsletters, simple UI | 12,000/month |
| **Mailchimp** | Audience management, campaigns | 500 contacts |
| **Twilio** | SMS + WhatsApp only (not email) | Pay per message |

### Common Email Issues
| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| Emails going to spam | Verify domain SPF/DKIM records in email service |
| "From" address rejected | Must use verified domain, not Gmail/Yahoo |
| Emails not sending in production | Check API key is set for production environment |
| Resend free tier | 3,000/month is enough for small/medium apps |

