## 🤖 AI MODEL INTEGRATIONS

### Comparison for Web Apps
| Model | Best For | Speed | Cost |
|---|---|---|---|
| **OpenAI GPT-4o** | Versatile, chat, content gen | Medium | High |
| **GPT-4o-mini** | Real-time chat, fast responses | Fast | Low |
| **Anthropic Claude** | Long context, nuanced, safe outputs | Medium | Medium |
| **Gemini** | Multimodal (text + image) | Fast | Medium |
| **Perplexity** | Search-augmented, cited answers | Medium | Low |

### Setup Pattern
1. Get API key from provider dashboard
2. Rocket chat: "Connect OpenAI to my project"
3. Paste API key
4. Prompt: "Add a chat interface powered by GPT-4o on the [page] page. Store conversation history in Supabase."

### Common AI Integration Issues
| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| 401 from AI API | API key wrong or expired — regenerate from provider |
| Rate limits | Free tier limits hit — upgrade API plan or add retry logic |
| Responses too slow | Use GPT-4o-mini or Gemini Flash for real-time chat |
| Response cut off | Increase `max_tokens` — ask Rocket: "increase max tokens for AI response" |
| AI going off-topic | Add system prompt — ask Rocket: "add a system prompt that limits AI to only discuss [topic]" |
| High API costs | Use streaming responses + set max_tokens limit |

