## 🗄️ DATABASES & CMS

### Supabase (Primary — see rocket-supabase.mdc for full details)
- PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage + Edge Functions
- Always the first choice for serious apps

### Airtable
- Use for: leads, CRM, internal tools, lightweight inventory
- Not for: complex relational data, high-volume production apps
- Free tier limit: 1,200 records/base

### Strapi / Directus (Headless CMS)
- Use for: content-heavy sites, blogs, multi-author publishing
- Requires separate hosting (not hosted inside Rocket)
- Connect via REST API in Rocket

