## 📊 ANALYTICS

### Google Analytics (GA4)
- Command: `/Setup Google Analytics use measurement ID G-XXXXXXX`
- Tracks: page views, user journeys, conversions, traffic sources
- Free, unlimited

### Mixpanel
- Better for: SaaS metrics, user behavior, conversion funnels, per-user analytics
- Free: 20M events/month

### Common Analytics Issues
| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| No data in GA4 | Check measurement ID format: G-XXXXXXX not UA-XXXXXXX |
| Events not firing | Ad blockers are blocking scripts — expected behavior, not a bug |
| GDPR cookie consent blocking analytics | Add consent check before initializing analytics |

