## 🎨 FIGMA INTEGRATION

### Setup
1. Figma → Share → Copy link → ensure "Anyone with link" = "Can view"
2. Start new Rocket project → "From Figma" → paste URL

### Best Practices for Import Quality
- Use auto-layout on all frames (not absolute positioning)
- Keep component nesting under 3 levels
- Use standard frame sizes: 1440px desktop, 1280px, 768px tablet, 375px mobile
- Name layers meaningfully: "Hero Section", "Nav Bar" — not "Frame 47"
- Export icons as SVG, not PNG

### Figma Troubleshooting
| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| "Same Figma URL already used" | Use different file, or delete old project using that URL |
| Not generating code | Check plan screen limit; check link permissions; rate limit → wait 10–15 min |
| Generated code looks wrong | Follow design guidelines above; simplify component nesting |
| Want to add new screens | "Add Figma screens" option (web only) |
| Want to update existing screens | Not supported yet — re-add screens or re-prompt in chat |

